Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.46,0:00:17.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's YOU who will die here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.33,0:00:19.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hero binding spell:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:21.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Anti-Leo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.79,0:00:33.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No! He's going to dodge it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.58,0:00:35.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've failed us all!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.38,0:00:39.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've protected no one, accomplished nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.50,0:00:43.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This is where I meet my end!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.58,0:00:53.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,(Thank you.)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.04,0:00:58.46,Song,,0,0,0,,Live, live on, with all your might
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.46,0:01:02.96,Song,,0,0,0,,Follow the light to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.71,0:01:16.83,Song,,0,0,0,,Betrayed and left behind in this lonely world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.17,0:01:22.38,Song,,0,0,0,,Fearing a tomorrow I've lost sight of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.88,0:01:25.50,Song,,0,0,0,,Ibasho o sagasu\NI search for the place I belong
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.50,0:01:32.00,Song,,0,0,0,,My heart screams out, "I want to be needed"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.21,0:01:40.75,Song,,0,0,0,,I want to puzzle out these entwined identities, but can I trust them?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.75,0:01:44.17,Song,,0,0,0,,Live, live on, with all your might
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.17,0:01:48.17,Song,,0,0,0,,Follow the light to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.50,0:01:51.67,Song,,0,0,0,,Even if you lose everything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.67,0:01:56.00,Song,,0,0,0,,Stay connected to hope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.21,0:01:59.71,Song,,0,0,0,,I don't know why I'm here
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.13,0:02:03.58,Song,,0,0,0,,But that's all right with me right now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.96,0:02:07.46,Song,,0,0,0,,I have to overcome and press on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.46,0:02:13.38,Song,,0,0,0,,So I can smile with you again
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.29,0:02:38.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Protect humanity from evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:40.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Protect humanity from evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.13,0:02:43.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Protect humanity from evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.04,0:02:46.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Protect humanity from evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.00,0:02:49.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Protect humanity from evil...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.04,0:02:49.67,Subtitle-2,,0,0,0,,Save the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.75,0:02:54.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I was to obey that order from the moment I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.54,0:03:07.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It was fine at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.46,0:03:11.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Just as Master Eibrad had said,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.71,0:03:14.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,the current world fulfilled my purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.83,0:03:17.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The people wanted what I had to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.25,0:03:20.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I fought alongside allies,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.71,0:03:22.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,defeated powerful foes,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.13,0:03:26.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and brought peace to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.92,0:03:32.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I was pure and innocent then, celebrating that peace\Nfrom the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.04,0:03:34.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.67,0:03:40.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The peace stretched on and on,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.50,0:03:43.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and the world found itself without need for a hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.92,0:03:47.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I no longer had a reason to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.21,0:04:12.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So there IS more for me to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.67,0:04:15.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Regional conflicts...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.08,0:04:20.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Guess humans and demons couldn't\Ncoexist peacefully after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.71,0:04:23.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wars between nations...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.46,0:04:28.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, you guys need to learn your lesson already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.92,0:04:31.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Then, an invasion from the Demon World.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.08,0:04:37.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I felt the world was telling me\Nthat I only deserved to live in it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:40.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,...when I was fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.13,0:04:44.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I can fight again. I can be a hero again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.67,0:04:46.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I can save humanity again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.38,0:04:50.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A hundred years passed, then two hundred.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:53.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Before I knew it, five hundred. A thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.38,0:04:56.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Then more, as time flowed endlessly on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.38,0:05:05.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I traveled the world, searching for battle,\Nfighting endlessly on...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.46,0:05:11.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,DH-05, Leo, was built around hyper skill development.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.46,0:05:15.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,With every enemy I fought,\NI would gain new techniques,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:19.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and eventually, I stopped encountering even matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:24.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I had become what the scientists who\Nmade me had wanted me to become:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:32.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,An unstoppable, unkillable, immortal bioweapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.50,0:05:41.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Then, once again, a long peace took hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.54,0:05:47.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Get your fresh-baked bread!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.17,0:05:49.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hello, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.46,0:05:50.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.67,0:05:52.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Goodness, only one?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:54.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yup, it's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.46,0:05:55.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We'll share it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:59.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Is that right? What good kids you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:01.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.58,0:06:02.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.17,0:06:03.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.04,0:06:04.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:05.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:06.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Come by again soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.25,0:06:10.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I hope this peaceful world lasts forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.42,0:06:16.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, why aren't you smiling? You're supposed to smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.13,0:06:19.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Smile and say "Me too".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.88,0:06:25.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Eventually, I realized there was a part of me\Nthat wanted the world to be in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.13,0:06:32.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I wanted every person,\Nevery lifeform on this planet, to need me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.42,0:06:37.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,To be in the same hopeless peril\Nit was when I was made.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.92,0:06:42.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I want to save the world. Please, let me save it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.71,0:06:44.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If I can't save the world, I'll lose myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.42,0:06:49.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Bring more danger to humanity!\NBring more chaos to the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.04,0:06:53.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Every day, more desire for destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.75,0:06:57.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Every day, more errors in my consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.13,0:07:07.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I could just do it myself. Plunge the world into peril.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.04,0:07:12.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's so obvious. Why didn't I think of it before?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.50,0:07:19.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The DH series had a feature that prevented\Nthe unit from bringing harm to humanity:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.63,0:07:24.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thought Masking. It prevented\Nthe unit from thinking harmful thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.54,0:07:31.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But developing a sense of self, growing an ego,\Nhad disabled its functionality for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.50,0:07:38.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And I knew how to do it. How to craft\Nthe perfect crisis for my world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.71,0:07:45.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Though I couldn't recreate the Akashic Engine,\NI made the Heroes the same as they were,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.04,0:07:49.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,three thousand years ago,\Nwhen they'd first saved humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.38,0:07:54.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's been too long, everyone. This is 05-Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.42,0:07:59.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It really has. Look how much I've changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:04.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You have a mission. Please give me a world to save.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:07.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Kill all of humanity,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:09.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,so I can protect them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.79,0:08:11.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,For I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.00,0:08:13.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,'Cause I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.13,0:08:16.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I still don't want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.50,0:08:18.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I still want to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.00,0:08:22.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I still want to be a hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.13,0:08:38.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Demons! Demons are attacking!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.96,0:08:39.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.13,0:08:42.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Inform the King at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:45.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Tell me what's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.46,0:08:48.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A huge portal opened up in the Seshat Mountains,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:49.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and demons started pouring through!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:51.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'll handle them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.17,0:08:56.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What was I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:30.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Well, damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.71,0:09:35.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I was going to destroy humanity for\Nmy own selfish satisfaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.00,0:09:39.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I was no hero. Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.92,0:09:43.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Only a demon would do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.33,0:09:46.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm the REAL Demon King here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.58,0:09:49.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Protect humanity from evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.46,0:09:53.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Protect humanity from evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.00,0:09:58.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That evil is HERE. I'M that evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.00,0:10:04.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The only surviving unit of the Demonhart Series, 05-Leo,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.67,0:10:09.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,was the greatest evil threatening the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:09.46,Subtitle-3,,0,0,0,,Protect humanity from evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:16.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'd destroy the world for my own selfish cause,\Ntoy with human lives to fulfill my own desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.54,0:10:19.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No Demon King could be more evil than I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.17,0:10:22.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Protect humanity from evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.50,0:10:28.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I know, I know. I've got a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.88,0:10:33.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's not like I haven't learned anything\Nthese last three thousand years!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.29,0:10:39.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Soon, I was setting off on a mission\Nto destroy the Demon Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.71,0:10:42.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I was the hero who would save the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.63,0:10:47.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I promise, I will defeat the Demon Queen and her army.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:54.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I had to quit heroing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.71,0:10:59.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I had to defeat evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.83,0:11:02.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't just be defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.33,0:11:07.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I needed to leave the Akashic Engine, the\NPhilosopher's Stone, to someone worthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.54,0:11:14.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,They had to be strong enough to defeat me,\Nto defend humanity in my stead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.79,0:11:17.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.83,0:11:21.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You heard my orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.42,0:11:24.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is an invasion,\Nbut we must avoid killing whenever possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.33,0:11:27.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Any territory we occupy must be ruled peacefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:29.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Is that understood?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.71,0:11:34.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Your Queen commands you!\NNo pillaging, no destruction, no arson!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:38.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And do NOT slaughter innocent civilians!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.04,0:11:42.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Remember, we did not come here to wage war!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.63,0:11:46.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Is an invasion not war?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.21,0:11:51.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yet that was the kind of Queen she was.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:56.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Fine, I'll talk, I'll talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.08,0:12:00.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Queen Echidna's just... kinda weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:05.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She invaded the human world 'cause she wants to make\Nthe Demon World a better place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.96,0:12:08.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There's never been a Demon King like her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.96,0:12:11.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've never met a woman as deserving of praise as her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:16.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She forbids us from doing unjust harm\Nto humans in the course of our invasion,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:21.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and she even stands on the front lines\Nto lead us into battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.79,0:12:26.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She hands out praise to everyone,\Neven us low-level imps!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.71,0:12:29.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Queen Echidna's a kind ruler!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.96,0:12:45.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Never would've guessed it'd be the Demon Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.13,0:12:53.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But this Echidna could have been\Nthe successor I'd been looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.38,0:12:58.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hell, she might be able to do more\Nthan just take my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.46,0:13:04.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She could become the bridge between the human and\Ndemon realms.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.54,0:13:06.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I should give her an interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.42,0:13:10.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But first, I should save the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.29,0:13:16.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That was the day I began my final journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.00,0:13:18.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I vow with all my honor as a warrior: you shall not pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.83,0:13:22.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Then I vow with all my honor as a hero that I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.79,0:13:29.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It was a journey to stop heroing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.71,0:13:31.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I will kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.79,0:13:33.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sure! Do it, if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.04,0:13:37.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A journey to kill the Hero Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:41.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't hurt Echidna!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.17,0:13:45.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Do you have a screw loose?! You've got\Nto be stupid to be asking me that right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.67,0:13:49.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'd find out what Echidna and\Nher Four Generals were all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.88,0:13:54.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I will see Queen Echidna's dreams realized. I will see\Npeace come to the Demon World!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.46,0:13:56.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And I will happily die for her cause!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.42,0:14:00.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Damn, you practically sound like the hero, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.67,0:14:04.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'd see if they were trustworthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.88,0:14:18.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So YOU are the Hero Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.42,0:14:22.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Queen Echidna, I'm here to see what you've got for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.67,0:14:32.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'd work for her, learn her thoughts and feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.17,0:14:37.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and determine if she was the right person\Nto whom to entrust my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:41.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And then, I would die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.75,0:14:47.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The Demon King must be defeated.\NThat's just how the world works.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.63,0:14:54.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,After three thousands years of life,\Nthe bug-riddled bioweapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.88,0:14:55.46,Subtitle-2,,0,0,0,,It's YOU who will die here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.46,0:14:58.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,...chose this absurd theatrical display
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:01.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,as his method of suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.21,0:15:05.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hero binding spell:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.33,0:15:07.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Anti-Leo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.04,0:15:17.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.42,0:15:20.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.21,0:15:28.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That smile... Was this what Leo wanted all along?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.88,0:15:46.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Every bone in my body is straining against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.21,0:15:49.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's ravaging me from the inside out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.42,0:15:57.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Unsurprising. I'm binding three\Nthousand years of power all by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.54,0:15:58.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This is my only chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.21,0:16:03.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I can only keep his power bound for six more seconds...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.46,0:16:07.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's been a long while since\NI've been in this much danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.08,0:16:10.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My body feels heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.50,0:16:12.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I can't even lift a finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:19.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The regeneration I'd learned from Virgo,\Nthe auto-counter I'd learned from Aquarius,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.29,0:16:24.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,the self-enhancements from Taurus and Cancer,\Nthe speed from Gemini...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:30.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Every last special ability of mine, blocked from use.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.38,0:16:36.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm the same weak 05-Leo I was at the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.88,0:16:42.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Time feels like it's moving in slow motion.\NLike my life's gonna flash before my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.75,0:16:46.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm finally going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.50,0:16:54.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She's in a lot of pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.17,0:17:00.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But I can see in her eyes that she knows\Nshe'll succeed, that her comrades will succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.58,0:17:05.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to say to me with those eyes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.38,0:17:08.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I had a premonition.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.88,0:17:14.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Queen Echidna, the Hero Leo is quickly fighting his\Nway through our soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.42,0:17:20.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,When I heard that name, and realized it\Nwas in the name of the spell, I had a feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.79,0:17:25.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But the King who had devised the spell,\NAstarot, did so hundreds of years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.29,0:17:29.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No human he fought back then could\Nbe alive today, or so I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.79,0:17:33.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But when Leo told me he was\Nborn during the Mechanical Age,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.25,0:17:38.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,that premonition became all but absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.42,0:17:42.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This hero has lived for three thousand years.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.92,0:17:48.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The hero who fought Astarot was the same hero\Nthat fought every other Demon King.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.33,0:17:52.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The names they called him may have been different,\Nbut it was only him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.96,0:17:57.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He had no friends, no place to return to, no place to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.38,0:18:02.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He would continue to live a lonely existence,\Nprotecting humanity all on his lonesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.04,0:18:05.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That is the fate of the Hero Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.58,0:18:08.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What's that look for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.63,0:18:11.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're fine. You've got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.33,0:18:15.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No one can do everything alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.63,0:18:19.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's why being able to trust others...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.83,0:18:24.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,is the one trait trait you need,\Nthe most important thing to have as a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.00,0:18:32.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I couldn't do that. I failed as a hero.\NI could never trust anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.13,0:18:36.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,How did it feel to fight through those eons?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.92,0:18:39.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why didn't he show weakness to anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.33,0:18:41.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why didn't he open his heart to anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.13,0:18:45.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I thought I had to be the one to protect the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.04,0:18:50.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That no one would accept me\Nif I decided to stop being the hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.88,0:18:55.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're so foolishly obsessed with your mission\Nthat you follow it to your death!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.96,0:19:01.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Do unto others as you would have them do unto you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.67,0:19:03.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Is that how the saying goes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.21,0:19:08.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wow. That's kinda funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.83,0:19:11.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,How could anyone find that funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:15.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I acted all high-and-mighty when I gave you advice...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.38,0:19:17.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You helped my Generals to the best of your ability...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.42,0:19:20.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But in the end, all I wanted...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.58,0:19:24.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,All I ever wanted...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.96,0:19:26.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But you must have wanted someone to save YOU!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.92,0:19:30.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,...was for someone to accept me for who I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.54,0:19:36.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,For someone to say they didn't care\Nif I wasn't the hero, to come with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.96,0:19:38.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,For someone to tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.50,0:19:40.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,that they'd save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.88,0:19:45.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He would let himself get this hurt,\Nall for the sake of protecting humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.33,0:19:48.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But who was protecting the hero?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:52.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,When he was suffering in the dark abyss,\Nwho offered him their hand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.38,0:19:57.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But it's okay. I'm glad I picked Echidna.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:20:00.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I picked them to be my last companions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.67,0:20:07.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I know that even if I die, they'll be able to bring\Nthe human and demon worlds together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.33,0:20:09.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're such a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.75,0:20:12.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Queen Echidna will not tolerate such foolishness!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.71,0:20:15.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I, WE, will offer you our hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.21,0:20:18.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I will put an end to this, here and now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.75,0:20:29.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,They're good people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.67,0:20:33.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I had fun working with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.13,0:20:38.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I wish I could've worked with them longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:44.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Dammit. I don't want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.58,0:20:50.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Leo, if you wish to die a hero's death,\Nthen I will grant it to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.67,0:20:53.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Here and now, I will end your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.21,0:20:56.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Great Generals, I leave the rest to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.25,0:21:04.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Lord Leo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.46,0:21:05.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.42,0:21:07.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Leo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:10.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Leo...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.67,0:21:20.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Bye, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.58,0:21:24.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I leave the rest to you.
